tests.de.susebox

Class TestExceptions

  • java.lang.Object
    • tests.de.susebox.TestExceptions

  • public class TestExceptions
extends java.lang.Object

    This class is a generic test for implementations of the ThrowableList interface. Instead of testing each implementation by its own, the common pattern of all these exceptions is used to define tests on all of them.

    Author:
    Heiko Blau
    See Also:
    ThrowableList
